                <h1>Continuous Background Checks: Ensuring Workplace Safety</h1>
                <p>Continuous background checks are essential for businesses aiming to maintain a safe, trustworthy work environment. By regularly updating employee records, companies can quickly identify any potential risks, such as criminal activity or changes in credit status. This proactive approach helps protect both the organization and its employees.</p>
